<p>The <b>International Federation of the Phonographic Industry</b> (<b>IFPI</b>) is the organization that represents the interests of the <a href="Recording_industry" title="Recording industry" class="mw-redirect">recording industry</a> worldwide. It is a not-for-profit members' organization registered in <a href="Switzerland" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. It operates a Secretariat based in <a href="London" title="London">London</a>, with regional offices in <a href="Brussels" title="Brussels">Brussels</a>, <a href="Hong_Kong" title="Hong Kong">Hong Kong</a> and <a href="Miami" title="Miami">Miami</a>.</p>
